data.description: This stunning, recently built one story home is located in the quiet community of Hazelwood. The home has  large lot with a nicely landscaped front yard a front porch and a 2 car driveway. It has an open spacious floorplan with luxury vinyl plank floors and ceilings lined with crown molding. Through the entryway there's an open and bright living room. This beautiful home features a dream kitchen with granite counters, soft close dove-tail cabinets, beautiful marble herringbone backsplash tile, brand new energy star stainless steel appliances and custom lighting. To the right of the the kitchen you will have a laundry area with a pantry and cabinets. To the left of the living room there is a full bathroom and 2 nice sized bedrooms. The large master bedroom is to the right with enough space for a king bed and all of your bedroom furniture. There's a large master bathroom with a tub & shower, vanity with quartz counters and a closet for your linens & large walk-in closet.
